data.description: This remodeled 3 bedroom, 3 bath home in a quiet country setting away from the hustle and bustle of the city.  This home should work equally well for empty nesters, or for a growing family.  The entire property has just been fenced, so you can have peace of mind if you have pets or young children.  There is a full RV hookup, with 200-amp service and a detached 10x16 shed. The home has a fireplace, new sheetrock, paint, electrical, lights, flooring and kitchen cabinets. It's getting hard to find anything in the country in this price range, unless it needs a lot of work, this home is move in ready.   Grab it and make it yours before someone else does.
